!! Variables via scope tiddler

''Prerequisite:'' create a tiddler titled `MyVars` with this content:

```
r: 5
h: 10
density: 2.7
```

Then:

| Expression | Result |h
| `œÄ * r^2` (circle area) | <$calc scope="MyVars">œÄ * r^2</$calc> |
| `œÄ * r^2 * h` (cylinder volume) | <$calc scope="MyVars">œÄ * r^2 * h</$calc> |
| `density * œÄ * r^2 * h` (mass) | <$calc scope="MyVars">density * œÄ * r^2 * h</$calc> |

